:normal;\" class=\"js_darkmode__1\" mpa-font-style=\"mjmai5mc7f5\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"511685369\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"width: 33px;height: 33px;background-color: transparent;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a1e1b406&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FpBxtubiaOffV2fsZ1tp4kYDFfJibjQg3F4gBPfib22qQ8CMTCB7XGFMWB71hcsJlI6u9a9Dqta5fAj0ckNCkUauEw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D2\"></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;每天一个提效AI工具，今天是推荐的第<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">35</span>款！</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-action-id&quot;:&quot;meje8fvtghk&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-mpa-action-id&quot;:&quot;mjmai5mn22u2&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;5 4 [\\&quot;para\\&quot;,{\\&quot;tagName\\&quot;:\\&quot;section\\&quot;,\\&quot;attributes\\&quot;:{\\&quot;data-mpa-action-id\\&quot;:\\&quot;meje8fvtghk\\&quot;,\\&quot;data-pm-slice\\&quot;:\\&quot;0 0 []\\&quot;},\\&quot;namespaceURI\\&quot;:\\&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\\&quot;}]&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;my-2 [&amp;+p]:mt-4 [&amp;_strong:has(+br)]:inline-block [&amp;_strong:has(+br)]:pb-2&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">StoryTribe直接拯救你的“画画焦虑”：它不用你学任何设计软件，只需像搭积木一样拖拽，就能做出专业级的漫画分镜。最绝的是它能用AI “无中生有”变出你缺的素材，还能让主角随意换表情、换动作但绝不“换脸”，让你的创意方案一眼就能被看懂，说服力直接拉满。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">①&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">智能角色“演播室” + 人设不崩</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">：</span>不想再用千篇一律的死板素材？你可以锁定同一个主角，随意切换他哭、笑、跑、跳几千种状态，人物长相始终如一，像导演一样控制演员，讲出来的故事连贯又生动。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">②&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">AI定制素材 + 风格零违和</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">：</span>自带库里找不到特定的道具？直接告诉Tribe AI，它能立马生成你想要的物品，而且画风和原版素材库完美融合，再也不用担心素材拼贴产生的“廉价感”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">③&nbsp;</span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">虚实场景融合 + 落地演示</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">：</span>支持直接上传你拍摄的真实环境照片（如办公室、商场）做背景，再把手绘人物放进去演示走位。这种“真实场景+虚拟演示”的混合模式，做汇报极其吸睛，特别适合视频策划和产品落地展示。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-sourcepos=\"26:1-26:95\" sourceposition=\"[object Object]\" node=\"[object Object]\" style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.51px;\"><strong class=\"js_darkmode__11\"><span leaf=\"\">工具获取见下图</span></strong><strong class=\"js_darkmode__12\"><span leaf=\"\">：</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mglpvn6djbg\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100061689\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"border-radius: 9px;background-color: transparent;height: auto !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_gif/DCCkl4hCZ4o65pLtfPTPHXNYwmicVXzkUrMc4GZBzB3RW9MEBVuUg9hcRicqxOm5xZMxTzecwFMib65S7lpgoEhsg/0?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"422\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3de7b57a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FDCCkl4hCZ4o65pLtfPTPHXNYwmicVXzkUrMc4GZBzB3RW9MEBVuUg9hcRicqxOm5xZMxTzecwFMib65S7lpgoEhsg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 5 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 0.51px;font-size: 15px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"511685364\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeho