8j910y0&quot;,&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mglqdzjc20m7&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">StoryTribe</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;my-2 [&amp;+p]:mt-4 [&amp;_strong:has(+br)]:inline-block [&amp;_strong:has(+br)]:pb-2&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 24px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">的帮助下，原本枯燥的文字方案能瞬间转化为生动有趣的连环画，极大地提升了沟通效率和提案成功率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mife59ly1imr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100063126\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5732484076433121\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"628\" style=\"border-radius:12px;background-color:transparent;width:586px;height:376px;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/DCCkl4hCZ4oZIxgD6RzpdicLb4DKC7URMqKbic742XNjpNyHR7QVQiaM6MID4Y813acbsg30lleoJuK2peD4GUnLA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"844\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=913a5a6a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FDCCkl4hCZ4oZIxgD6RzpdicLb4DKC7URMqKbic742XNjpNyHR7QVQiaM6MID4Y813acbsg30lleoJuK2peD4GUnLA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;font-size: 15px;\">StoryTribe</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"minztoid1e4p\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;font-size: 15px;\">特</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"minztoid1e4p\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;font-size: 15px;\">色功能</span><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"minztoid1e4p\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;font-size: 15px;\">与特点</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;font-size: 15px;\">1. 智能角色演播室</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.51px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">告别千篇一律的死板素材。在这里，你可以像导演一样控制角色。同一个人物模型，支持数千种表情、姿势和服装的自由组合。你可以让主角在第一页大笑，第二页思考，人物形象始终保持统一，完美适配连续的故事情节。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;font-size: 15px;\">2. Tribe AI 创意补给站</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.51px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">找不到合适的道具？没关系。其内置的Tribe AI功能允许你直接用自然语言描述需求，比如“一个破旧的复古闹钟”或“一只正在睡觉的猫”。AI会生成与自带素材库画风完全一致的线稿元素，无缝融入你的画面，彻底解决了“找素材找半天”的难题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;font-size: 15px;\">3. 实景增强混合模式</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.51px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">这是它非常“实战派”的一个功能。你可以上传手机拍摄的真实环境照片（如会议室、商场、街道）作为背景，然后将虚拟的手绘人物放置其中进行演示。这种“真实背景+虚拟演示”的表现形式，非常适合用来制作落地执行方案或视频拍摄计划。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;font-size: 15px;\">4. 专业级演示与导出</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.51px;font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">做好的故事板不仅支持生成高清晰度的PDF文档，还能直接作为演示文稿分享。针对视频工作者，它甚至支持添加镜头运动标记、注释和场景编号，直接导出就是一份标准的工业级分镜脚本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 0.51px;font-size: 15px;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"511685364\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" style=\"width: 34px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=60de69d6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FpBxtubiaOffV2fsZ1tp4kYDFfJibjQg3F4ZUWWm1rXyIr5do6Zv1PRC7ibUS3UhA5cmViaqzpTB1XpeWNcGibT5Nv7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D18\">&nbsp;</span></strong><span data-mpa-action-id=\"mc9zq14m1dfe\"><strong><span style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 0.51px;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">后台经常有小伙伴问我们</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">优设是否有群，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">其实优设有许多，我们运营已有</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">13</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">年啦。</span></span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 5 []\"><span data-mpa-action-id=\"mc9zq14m1dfe\"><strong><span style=\"text-align: justify;letter-spacing: 0.51px;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">群内严格管理，每天分享行业动态和AI技巧，同时也会提供作品集探讨与大厂内推工作机会。</span></span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 5 []\"><span style=\"font-weight: b